// ║  VAS / Kitting                            ~1136–1185                       ║
// ║  Task Interleaving                        ~1187–1240                       ║
// ║  Slotting Optimization                    ~1242–1312                       ║
// ║  Cartonization & Manifesting              ~1314–1365                       ║
// ║  Returns / RMA                            ~1367–1457                       ║
// ║  Labor Management                         ~1459–1528                       ║
// ║  Yard & Dock Scheduling                   ~1530–1685                       ║
// ║  Compliance & Customs                     ~1687–1724                       ║
// ║  LPN / Container Tracking                 ~1726–1766                       ║
// ║  Cross-Dock Orchestration                 ~1768–1805                       ║
// ║  Automation & Robotics                    ~1807–1861                       ║
// ║  Document Intelligence (DocAI)            ~1863–1906                       ║
// ║  Transfer Orders (Multi-Warehouse)        ~1908–1958                       ║
